



Object-Oriented
Programming(Classes,Objects)

class :
		class is nothing but it is a one design
										Designs
	-->a class is a specification (idea/plan/theory)
	of properties and actions of objects
	-->varaibles(properties) and methods (actions)
	
example:
	Design
			construct house
			
			
		plan-->design(2bedrooms,1 kichen,one hall,2 balc,parking etc)
				
			design:
					house1-->2bedrooms,1 kichen,one hall,2 
					house2-->2bedrooms,1 kichen,one hall,2 
					house3-->2bedrooms,1 kichen,one hall,2 
				
			
sytax:
	class classname:
		varaibles
		methods

method:funtion with in class we are call it is  method
def myfun():# function
	print("Hello")
class Demo:
	myvar1=10
	myvar2=20
	def myfun1(self): # method
		print("Hello")
	def myfun2(self):
		print("Hi hello")
		
Demo.myvar1
	10
Demo.myvar2
	20
Demo.myfun1()
	Hello
Demo.myfun2()
	Hi hello

object:
	instace of class variables and methods
	grouped items
	syatax:
		obj=classname()
		obj.myvar1
		obj.myvar2
		obj.myfun1
		obj.myfun2
	
	
